pip install:
    streamlit
    python-dotenv
    fastapi 
    uvicorn
    langchain 
    langchain-openai 
    langchain-core 
    langchain-community 
    docx2txt 
    pypdf  
    langchain_chroma 
    sentence-transformers

Development Run:
    uvicorn api.main:app --reload
    streamlit run app/streamlit_app.py

    Check FastAPI: http://127.0.0.1:8000/docs
    Streamlit UI:  http://localhost:8501/

Production Run:
    Build Command: pip install -r requirements.txt
    Start Command: ./start.sh
    
(setup for a render webservice)


Main Changelog:
12/7/24 - Added default document upload and protections at streamlit frontend (sidebar) and API backend in main.py and db_tils.py

